sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client (ADMIN)
    participant E as Express API
    participant PM as PermissionMiddleware
    participant MS as MessageService
    participant R as ServerMemberRepo

    C->>E: DELETE /api/messages/:id
    E->>PM: authenticate + requireAdmin
    PM-->>E: Authorized (is Admin)
    E->>MS: deleteMessage(adminId, messageId)
    MS->>R: findByUserAndServer(authorId, serverId)
    R-->>MS: role: 'OWNER'
    Note over MS: Logic: ADMIN cannot<br/>delete OWNER's message
    MS-->>E: throw ForbiddenError
    E-->>C: Response 403 { success: false, message: "..." }